text: Ioesse sanguinolenta is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by James Thomson in 1864. It is known from Malaysia.BioLib.cz - Ioesse sanguinolenta. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1864
